content.html: There are Tory MPs in Church today, dressed in their Sunday best. They will listen to The Good Samaritan parable and likely proclaim peace and love to all. Tomorrow they will go back to supporting the deportation of the most vulnerable & traumatised people to Rwanda.
content.value:
There are Tory MPs in Church today, dressed in their Sunday best. 

They will listen to The Good Samaritan parable and likely proclaim peace and love to all. 

Tomorrow they will go back to supporting the deportation of the most vulnerable & traumatised people to Rwanda.
